<h5 id=3D"MapLocationFieldType-Constructor">Constructor</h5>
<p><span>The <strong><code>MapLocation</code></strong></span><strong><code>=
\Value</code></strong><span>&nbsp;constructor will&nbsp;initialize a new Va=
lue object with the values provided. Two floats and a string are expected.<=
br></span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Constructor example</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">// Instantiates a MapLocation Value object
$MapLocationValue =3D new MapLocation\Value( 59.928732, 10.777888, "eZ Syst=
ems Norge" );</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"MapLocationFieldType-Templaterendering">Template rendering</h2>
<p>The template called by <a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/Content+Rendering#C=
ontentRendering-ez_render_field">the <strong>ez_render_field()</strong> Twi=
g function</a> while rendering a Map Location field accepts the following t=
he parameters:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Parameter</th>
<th colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Default</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>mapType</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>string</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>"ROADMAP"</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><a href=3D"https://developers.google.com/maps/do=
cumentation/javascript/maptypes#BasicMapTypes" class=3D"external-link" rel=
=3D"nofollow">One of the GMap type of map</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>showMap</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>boolean</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>true</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Whether to show a Google Map</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>showInfo</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>booolean</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>true</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">Whether to show a latitude, longit=
ude and the address outside of the map</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>zoom</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>integer</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>13</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">The initial zoom level on the map<=
/td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>draggable</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>boolean</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>true</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span class=3D"c">Whether to en=
able draggable map<br></span></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>width</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>string|false</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>"500px"</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span class=3D"c">The width of =
the rendered map with its unit (for example "500px" or "50em"),</span> <spa=
n class=3D"c">set to false to not set any width style inline.</span></p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>height</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>string|false</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>"200px"</code></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span class=3D"c">The height of=
 the rendered map with its unit (for example "200px" or "20em"),</span> <sp=
an class=3D"c">set to false to not set any height style inline.</span></p><=
/td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">scrollWheel</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span>boolean</span></td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd">true</td>
<td colspan=3D"1" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lo=
zenge aui-lozenge-current">&gt;=3D1.7.1</span> Allows you to disable scroll=
 wheel starting to zoom when mouse comes over the map as user scrolls down =
a page.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p>Example:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">{{ ez_render_field(content, 'location', {'parameters': {'width': '1=
00%', 'height': '330px', 'showMap': true, 'showInfo': false}}) }}</pre>=20
</div>
